&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://docs.docker.com/compose/startup-order/">https://docs.docker.com/compose/startup-order/&lt;/a>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Nextcloud in Docker</title><link>https://www.danaukes.com/notebook/docker/nextcloud/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.danaukes.com/notebook/docker/nextcloud/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="docker-compose">docker-compose&lt;/h2>
